Joanne Linville https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joanne_Linville 0 Beverly Joanne Linville (born January 15, 1928) is a retired American film and television actress. Linville and actress Irene Gilbert co-founded the Stella Adler Academy in Los Angeles in 1985. Beverly_Joanne_Linville ( born January_15_,_1928 ) is a_retired_American_film_and_television_actress . Linville_and_actress_Irene_Gilbert co-founded the_Stella_Adler_Academy in Los_Angeles in 1985 .
